{"tid":2009521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"聯署都唔係濫竽充數","createTime":"2020-05-09T19:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T09:17:10.000Z","uid":79161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9383ac8b10bb093a79a936dbed30568c6f385daa","tid":2009521,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T19:17:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hker-hope-usa-add-hk-security-staff-legislative-council-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-sanctions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhker-hope-usa-add-hk-security-staff-legislative-council-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-sanctions&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=98a7f9ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hker-hope-usa-add-hk-security-staff-legislative-council-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-sanctions</a><br />\n<br />\npetition貴精不貴多<br />\n2萬幾人簽呢個petition<br />\n當中有幾多人聯署係純粹為左聯署？<br />\n又大楷，又全形逗號，又冇proofread<br />\n其實寫番篇睇得順眼啲嘅真係唔難<br />\n然後話要制裁啲保安<br />\n但係講埋冇name list呢句<br />\n成件事望落都幾兒戲<br />\n我唔評論你想制裁保安呢個motive<br />\n但係真係交代多啲啲個原因<br />\n可能例如點濫權又 correlate to the act 咁樣<br />\n<br />\n都唔評論petition嘅影響力喇<br />\n不過要draw attention 就實有 attention fatigue<br />\n如果幾百個petition都係咁質素<br />\n人地仲理唔理你<br />\n<br />\n我只係想知簽嘅呢2萬幾人<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">係有冇睇過內容先簽？<br />\n定係睇咗覺得ok，最緊要標題講左個要求？</span><br />\n或者可能大家覺得冇咩問題嘅話<br />\n係我太bitchy 就俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n順手click入去簽咗佢 當係我免費宣傳算"},{"pid":"3f3845319c7593de1981fbd5e048929bfc449281","tid":2009521,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}